&lt;p&gt;Quantum Coffee is a meeting place, a community centre and a destination for quality coffee. Quantum Coffee employees work to anticipate and fulfill customer needs, ensuring a welcoming environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Barista, you will work at various stations throughout the coffee bar, and will work with all others in the coffee bar during your scheduled shifts.&amp;nbsp; Baristas report to the Manager and Shift Supervisors as required.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Barista responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Craft specialty coffee beverages and serve baked goods&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use Point-Of-Sale (POS) system and handle cash accurately&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interact with customers, maintain customer service standard&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain safe and healthy work environments by following company standard operating procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restock supplies, detail oriented.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills and ability to multitask in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cleaning of coffee machines and equipment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A positive attitude, a smile and a passion for coffee&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High volume experience, being able to work on multiple orders at once&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Outgoing personality with strong work ethic&lt;/li&gt;
